{
  "text": "In view of the fact that anxiety is highly prevalent 45.2% in reflux diseases like NERD compared to healthy patients [CITATION_1] , and may contribute to PPI failure, it is reasonable to prefer fixed dose combination of amitriptyline and pantoprazole in the management of GERD with coexisting anxiety.",
